name: Kiefer Sutherland | Sailor dad
bio: Mahalo! I'm Kiefer Sutherland | Sailor dad. I'm a Dogwalker by day, and I like prank-calling celebrities by night. I once dreamed of being a Skydiving Instructor. Now I can be found pole dancing all day. I can't wait to wake you up at 4am for seemingly no reason.
